Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.29,0:00:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎能夠理解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.63,0:00:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞．舒恩伯格製造Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.50,0:00:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 製造GN Drive的緣由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.59,0:00:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武力介入是為此鋪路的基石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞的目的是將人類引向新紀元
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.77,0:00:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.23,0:00:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正面臨著變革
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變革？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.57,0:00:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,造就是你達到的極限嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.41,0:00:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天人再次…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時請務必給我戰鬥的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,復仇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我所追求的是戰鬥之人才能到達的極限
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:00:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少年曾說我扭曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而 他也是只能戰鬥的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.06,0:01:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才渴求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.99,0:01:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那極限的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.95,0:01:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只渴望勝利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.91,0:01:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此外還有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.70,0:01:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還用問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.25,0:01:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有通向未來的…明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.92,0:01:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格殺勿論
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空手入白刃？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是 我的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥吧 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.76,0:02:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將我劈開 親手獲得勝利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.27,0:02:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為何不給我致命一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活著抓住明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.36,0:02:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為生存而戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈 路易斯．阿勒威的機體呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.42,0:02:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒反應 應該是撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:02:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:02:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是想謝你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為純種覺醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那．F．清英
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是掌握人類命運的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道Veda所在了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 王留美給的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:04:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到Veda了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暗號解析完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,座標是CZ9842R
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月球背面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜 用超望遠攝像機捕捉座標
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L2
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未進行殖民地開發的地點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要藏身再適合不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顯示座標
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將這個位置的天體圖重疊上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星體的位置偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光學迷彩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲爾德 計算出有偏差的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直徑15公里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,15公里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要如此隱藏的物體…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在月球背面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐 實驗室的運輸艦發來暗號通信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新裝備來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獨立治安維持部隊A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總動員開始殲滅天人作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打倒他們這反政府勢力最後的要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為統一世界贏來真正的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,期待諸位奮勇作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,21艘巡洋艦加108架MS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有這麼多兵力…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准將
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特許員脫離了艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別理他們 要在戰場上肆意妄為可受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利馮茲發來了返航命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他終於下定決心了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 一切按計劃進行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:06:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該來的已經逼近了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯．阿勒威
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為家人報仇？我又何嘗不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以為天下就你可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活該
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能作為戰鬥力的都帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam各機的強化組件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有托勒密的補充物資
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連0-Gundam都有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安裝了粒子儲存罐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以在一定時間內進行戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 盡快搬入
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王留美指定的座標有艦隊集結
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Veda就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有變革者的大本營
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要突破A-LAWS艦隊 奪回Veda
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.06,0:08:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會是前所未有的激戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去 為了完成我的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫斯洛德君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我決定了 不再猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也參加
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,索瑪．比利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也有參戰的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 雖然目的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們都有奔赴戰場的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而這意志通往未來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要為未來而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了從變革者的支配下解放人類
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓我和索瑪．比利斯這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不再出現在世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的任務是打倒聯邦政府
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要狙擊變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要變革
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不變革就無法面對未來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,補給完成後就發動托勒密
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在托勒密沒有操舵員…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.56,0:09:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然能行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去月球那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉娜殿下 好多星星哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:09:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 真美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家 要懂禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS正在L2集結艦隊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-1發來的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天人也打算前往
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政變派發來了同樣的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,附帶詳細的戰術計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,配置完畢 上校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於要進行審判了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是變革為純種的剎那．F．清英 還是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二者選一決定人類命運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂武士道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是追尋死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為生存而戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂武士道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超遠距離光學探測器捕捉到敵人艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全員 一級戰鬥戒備
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲爾德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說是琳達小姐在實驗室培育的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.57,0:11:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想…送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.33,0:11:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 菲爾德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會惹瑪莉娜陛下生氣吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和她並非那種關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:11:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去Gundam那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:11:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別死啊 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密 全部閘門打開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誓要奪回Veda
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指引我吧 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾迪 期待你的戰果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee 提耶利亞．艾迪出發
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備好嗎 索瑪．比利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗就行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想這樣稱呼我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Archer Arios
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亞．哈普提森
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,索瑪．比利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝目標飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim 出擊準備完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:13:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐 看我的
