Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狙擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確定嗎 沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必為我擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想自己把握未來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,00 剎那．F．清英 出動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0-Raiser 沙慈．庫斯洛德出擊
