Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.22,0:14:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壓縮粒子 全面釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新傢伙還真好使
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦依舊沒有減速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自殺攻擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那對敵艦隊使用Raiser Sword
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raiser系統啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM Raiser
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,粒子干擾？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反粒子領域被大範圍擴散
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,粒子光束效力低下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:16:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總比讓它們近身好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改變軌道 脫離影響範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.42,0:16:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應對得倒也算快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主力部隊開火 以數量壓倒他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 粒子光束被…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,導彈殘彈…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人數量過多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左舷中彈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,損傷情況…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 亂拳打死老師傅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵機逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總算來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katharon
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掩護天人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,援軍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katharon嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來得好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katharon的武裝…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預測到反粒子領域作戰？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.62,0:18:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓托勒密開向敵艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 Katharon？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們那點兵力…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:18:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准將 我軍的運輸艦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,運輸艦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.59,0:19:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,粒子光束攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通知A-LAWS艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.27,0:19:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在此揭竿而起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,淪為聯邦暴政傀儡的A-LAWS已非軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界的未來取決於民意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們將為自己的野蠻行徑付出代價
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並接受人民的審判
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那隻狐狸精…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鎮壓！他們是反政府勢力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人部隊正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MS部隊開始攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不死之身的戈拉索瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:19:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前來拜訪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對付運輸艦為何如此狼狽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它們躲在僚艦身後 無法攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.38,0:20:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊不需要累贅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連同敵艦一起擊沉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦上還有友軍士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我命令你開火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准將 敵艦突破了反粒子領域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.15,0:20:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,00-Raiser 驅逐目標
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快想辦法！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.93,0:22:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好壯觀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.52,0:22:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯他們正在戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.27,0:22:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭之光…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.28,0:22:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS艦隊被突破…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.82,0:22:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來人類挺喜歡戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.12,0:22:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不正是你一手安排的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.00,0:23:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引領他們走到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.00,0:23:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這應該也是你的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.54,0:23:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.42,0:23:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.67,0:23:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是你們的上等種族
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.26,0:23:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可稱之為創造主
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.22,0:23:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你的狼子野心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.97,0:23:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早已透過腦量子波讓我精晰可聞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.27,0:23:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜了 雷傑尼．雷傑塔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.41,0:23:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利馮茲．阿爾馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.29,0:23:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我…只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.26,0:23:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠引導人類的只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.30,0:23:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷傑尼．雷傑塔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.31,0:24:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變革者的大型母艦終於顯露崢嶸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.35,0:24:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meister們勝算幾何
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.65,0:24:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集 生命之華
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.15,0:24:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生命如同戰場之光轉瞬即逝
